<L>__{interior storeroom night}
<A>__{nick, leaning against the wall, watches the girl's apartment across the street. the girl walks in, turns on her light, then disappears into the bathroom. ich walks in, exhausted, soaked to the skin. he tosses his cap in the corner. struck out again.}
<C>__{ich}
<D>__{work, lunch, groceries, laundry... fabulous...}
